3/*++
4/* NAME
5/* cleanup_state 3
6/* SUMMARY
7/* per-message state variables
8/* SYNOPSIS
9/* #include "cleanup.h"
10/*
11/* CLEANUP_STATE *cleanup_state_alloc(src)
12/* VSTREAM *src;
13/*
14/* void cleanup_state_free(state)
15/* CLEANUP_STATE *state;
16/* DESCRIPTION
17/* This module maintains about two dozen state variables
18/* that are used by many routines in the course of processing one
19/* message.
20/*
21/* cleanup_state_alloc() initializes the per-message state variables.
22/*
23/* cleanup_state_free() cleans up.
24/* LICENSE
25/* .ad
26/* .fi
27/* The Secure Mailer license must be distributed with this software.
28/* AUTHOR(S)
29/* Wietse Venema
30/* IBM T.J. Watson Research
31/* P.O. Box 704
32/* Yorktown Heights, NY 10598, USA
33/*--*/
34
35/* System library. */
36
37#include <sys_defs.h>
38
39/* Utility library. */
40
41#include <mymalloc.h>
42#include <vstring.h>
43#include <htable.h>
44
45/* Global library. */
46
47#include <been_here.h>
48#include <mail_params.h>
49#include <mime_state.h>
50#include <mail_proto.h>
51
52/* Milter library. */
53
54#include <milter.h>
55
56/* Application-specific. */
57
58#include "cleanup.h"
59
60/* cleanup_state_alloc - initialize global state */
61
62CLEANUP_STATE *cleanup_state_alloc(VSTREAM *src)
63{
64 CLEANUP_STATE *state = (CLEANUP_STATE *) mymalloc(sizeof(*state));
65
66 state->attr_buf = vstring_alloc(10);
67 state->temp1 = vstring_alloc(10);
68 state->temp2 = vstring_alloc(10);
69 if (cleanup_strip_chars)
70 state->stripped_buf = vstring_alloc(10);
71 state->src = src;
72 state->dst = 0;
73 state->handle = 0;
74 state->queue_name = 0;
75 state->queue_id = 0;
76 state->arrival_time.tv_sec = state->arrival_time.tv_usec = 0;
77 state->fullname = 0;
78 state->sender = 0;
79 state->recip = 0;
80 state->orig_rcpt = 0;
81 state->return_receipt = 0;
82 state->errors_to = 0;
83 state->auto_hdrs = argv_alloc(1);
84 state->hbc_rcpt = 0;
85 state->flags = 0;
86 state->tflags = 0;
87 state->qmgr_opts = 0;
88 state->errs = 0;
89 state->err_mask = 0;
90 state->headers_seen = 0;
91 state->hop_count = 0;
92 state->resent = "";
93 state->dups = been_here_init(var_dup_filter_limit, BH_FLAG_FOLD);
94 state->action = cleanup_envelope;
95 state->data_offset = -1;
96 state->body_offset = -1;
97 state->xtra_offset = -1;
98 state->cont_length = 0;
99 state->sender_pt_offset = -1;
100 state->sender_pt_target = -1;
101 state->append_rcpt_pt_offset = -1;
102 state->append_rcpt_pt_target = -1;
103 state->append_hdr_pt_offset = -1;
104 state->append_hdr_pt_target = -1;
105 state->append_meta_pt_offset = -1;
106 state->append_meta_pt_target = -1;
107 state->milter_hbc_checks = 0;
108 state->milter_hbc_reply = 0;
109 state->rcpt_count = 0;
110 state->reason = 0;
111 state->smtp_reply = 0;
112 state->attr = nvtable_create(10);
113 nvtable_update(state->attr, MAIL_ATTR_LOG_ORIGIN, MAIL_ATTR_ORG_LOCAL);
114 state->mime_state = 0;
115 state->mime_errs = 0;
116 state->hdr_rewrite_context = MAIL_ATTR_RWR_LOCAL;
117 state->filter = 0;
118 state->redirect = 0;
119 state->dsn_envid = 0;
120 state->dsn_ret = 0;
121 state->dsn_notify = 0;
122 state->dsn_orcpt = 0;
123 state->verp_delims = 0;
124 state->milters = 0;
125 state->client_name = 0;
126 state->reverse_name = 0;
127 state->client_addr = 0;
128 state->client_af = 0;
129 state->client_port = 0;
130 state->milter_ext_from = 0;
131 state->milter_ext_rcpt = 0;
132 state->milter_err_text = 0;
133 state->free_regions = state->body_regions = state->curr_body_region = 0;
134 state->smtputf8 = 0;
135 return (state);
136}
137
138/* cleanup_state_free - destroy global state */
139
140void cleanup_state_free(CLEANUP_STATE *state)
141{
142 vstring_free(state->attr_buf);
143 vstring_free(state->temp1);
144 vstring_free(state->temp2);
145 if (cleanup_strip_chars)
146 vstring_free(state->stripped_buf);
147 if (state->fullname)
148 myfree(state->fullname);
149 if (state->sender)
150 myfree(state->sender);
151 if (state->recip)
152 myfree(state->recip);
153 if (state->orig_rcpt)
154 myfree(state->orig_rcpt);
155 if (state->return_receipt)
156 myfree(state->return_receipt);
157 if (state->errors_to)
158 myfree(state->errors_to);
159 argv_free(state->auto_hdrs);
160 if (state->hbc_rcpt)
161 argv_free(state->hbc_rcpt);
162 if (state->queue_name)
163 myfree(state->queue_name);
164 if (state->queue_id)
165 myfree(state->queue_id);
166 been_here_free(state->dups);
167 if (state->reason)
168 myfree(state->reason);
169 if (state->smtp_reply)
170 myfree(state->smtp_reply);
171 nvtable_free(state->attr);
172 if (state->mime_state)
173 mime_state_free(state->mime_state);
174 if (state->filter)
175 myfree(state->filter);
176 if (state->redirect)
177 myfree(state->redirect);
178 if (state->dsn_envid)
179 myfree(state->dsn_envid);
180 if (state->dsn_orcpt)
181 myfree(state->dsn_orcpt);
182 if (state->verp_delims)
183 myfree(state->verp_delims);
184 if (state->milters)
185 milter_free(state->milters);
186 if (state->milter_ext_from)
187 vstring_free(state->milter_ext_from);
188 if (state->milter_ext_rcpt)
189 vstring_free(state->milter_ext_rcpt);
190 if (state->milter_err_text)
191 vstring_free(state->milter_err_text);
192 cleanup_region_done(state);
193 myfree((void *) state);
194}
